   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>Organizations generally run survey poll to learn about their customers' choices and trends while making a strategic decision, such as, launching a new service in highly-interested customer segments.</p>
<h3 id="id-(4.3)Forms-CallbackForms"><span id="Forms-CallbackForms"></span>Callback Forms
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/forms#id-(4.3)Forms-CallbackForms">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>A callback form is usually built for website visitors to leave a callback request if they don't want to wait for an agent in queues. You may create different callback forms based on the page the customer visited.</p>
<h3 id="id-(4.3)Forms-Wrap-upForms"><span id="Forms-Wrap-upForms"></span>Wrap-up Forms&nbsp;
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/forms#id-(4.3)Forms-Wrap-upForms">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>A wrap-up form is designed by a business administrator to define wrap-up reasons that it wants its agents to choose from. You may want to design multiple forms each having different wrap-up reasons, for example, to segregate wrap-ups based on call type, Inbound/Outbound, campaign, queue, etc.&nbsp;</p>
<p>With the Form object, you can create as many wrap-up forms as needed.</p>
<h3 id="id-(4.3)Forms-Complaintregistration"><span id="Forms-Complaintregistration"></span>Complaint registration
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
